Class SQLScript

Comparable<SQLScript>
public class SQLScript
extends Object
implements Comparable<SQLScript>

Domain object to model a jcatapult SQL script. All jcatapult scripts will have the following naming convention: Version-Label.sql Where Version is a Major, Minor, or Patch number and the Label is any arbitrary set of characters describing the sql file. Ex: 1.0-seed-for-table-x.sql JCatapult SQL Scripts will also be of a certain type, where the type refers to whether it's a base, alter, or seed script User: jhumphrey Date: Dec 12, 2007
